Rusesabagina ni wa munyarwanda uvugwa muri '''Filimi yitwa Hotel Rwanda''' aho bavuga ko yagiriye neza impunzi zari zarahungiye muri Hotel yari akuriye yitwa Mille Collines mu gihe cya [[Jenoside y’Abatutsi muri Mata 1994]]. Gusa bamwe mu baharokokeye bemeza ko atari ineza yabagiriye ahubwo yabafatiranye n’ingorane bari barimo maze abavanamo ifaranga ritubutse. Nyuma rero y’aho iriya filimi itemeranywaho na bose isohokeye yahise abyuririraho maze yiyitirira ubutwari benshi bemeza ko butigeze bumurangwaho. Bwana Bagabe  Dan ni umugabo twahuriye mu iguriro ryitwa Nakumatt hano i Kigali maze ambwira ko uriya mugabo akwiriye kwitwa intwari yakorewe i [[Burayi]] ( ''A hero made in Europe''). Impamvu atanga n’uko ubutwari bwe butemerwa n’abanyarwanda avuga ko yabukoreye.

